TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAIN.ORG_LSTNODEID AS ORG_LSTNODEID, MAIN.ORG_NODEID AS ORG_NODEID, MAIN.ADMINID AS ADMINID FROM (SELECT (SELECT O.ORG_NODEID FROM ORG_NODE_DIM O WHERE O.ORG_NODE_LEVEL = S.LST_ORG_NODE_LEVEL AND O.ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH = S.LST_ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH AND O.CUSTOMERID = S.CUSTOMERID) AS ORG_LSTNODEID, (SELECT O.ORG_NODEID FROM ORG_NODE_DIM O WHERE O.ORG_NODE_LEVEL = S.ORG_NODE_LEVEL AND O.ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH = S.ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH AND O.CUSTOMERID = S.CUSTOMERID) AS ORG_NODEID, (SELECT A.ADMINID FROM ADMIN_DIM A WHERE A.IS_CURRENT_ADMIN = 'Y') AS ADMINID FROM STG_ORG_LSTNODE_LINK S) MAIN WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT NULL FROM ORG_LSTNODE_LINK L WHERE L.ORG_LSTNODEID = MAIN.ORG_LSTNODEID AND L.ORG_NODEID = MAIN.ORG_NODEID AND L.ADMINID = MAIN.ADMINID)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT OND.ORG_NODEID AS ORG_NODEID, MAIN.ORG_NODE_NAME AS ORG_NODE_NAME, MAIN.ORG_NODE_LABEL AS ORG_NODE_LABEL, MAIN.ORG_NODE_CODE AS ORG_NODE_CODE, MAIN.ORG_NODE_LEVEL AS ORG_NODE_LEVEL, MAIN.STRC_ELEMENT AS STRC_ELEMENT, MAIN.SPECIAL_CODES AS SPECIAL_CODES, MAIN.ORG_MODE AS ORG_MODE, MAIN.PARENT_ORG_LEVEL AS PARENT_ORG_LEVEL, MAIN.PARENT_ORG_CODE AS PARENT_ORG_CODE, MAIN.ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH AS ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH, MAIN.EMAIL_1 AS EMAIL, MAIN.CUSTOMER_ID AS CUSTOMER_ID, DECODE(OND.ORG_NODEID, NULL, 'I', 'U') AS INSERT_UPDATE_FLAG FROM (SELECT S.ORG_NODE_NAME AS ORG_NODE_NAME, S.ORG_NODE_LABEL AS ORG_NODE_LABEL, S.ORG_NODE_CODE AS ORG_NODE_CODE, S.ORG_NODE_LEVEL AS ORG_NODE_LEVEL, S.STRC_ELEMENT AS STRC_ELEMENT, S.SPECIAL_CODES AS SPECIAL_CODES, S.ORG_MODE AS ORG_MODE, S.PARENT_ORG_LEVEL AS PARENT_ORG_LEVEL, S.PARENT_ORG_CODE AS PARENT_ORG_CODE, S.ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH AS ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH, S.EMAIL_1 AS EMAIL_1, S.CUSTOMER_ID AS CUSTOMER_ID FROM STG_ORG_NODE_DIM S) MAIN, (SELECT S.ORG_NODEID, S.ORG_NODE_CODE, S.ORG_NODE_LEVEL, S.CUSTOMERID, S.ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH FROM ORG_NODE_DIM S WHERE S.CUSTOMERID IN (SELECT DISTINCT CUSTOMER_ID FROM STG_ORG_NODE_DIM)) OND WHERE MAIN.ORG_NODE_CODE = OND.ORG_NODE_CODE(+) AND MAIN.ORG_NODE_LEVEL = OND.ORG_NODE_LEVEL(+) AND MAIN.CUSTOMER_ID = OND.CUSTOMERID(+) AND MAIN.ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH = OND.ORG_NODE_CODE_PATH(+) ORDER BY MAIN.ORG_NODE_LEVEL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT USER_ID_SEQ.NEXTVAL AS USER_ID, X.ORG_NODEID, X.ORG_NODE_LEVEL, CASE WHEN X.ORG_NODE_LEVEL = 1 Then X.USER_NAME Else LOWER(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTR(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(X.FULLNAME, ' ', ''), '.', ''), '-', ''), '_', ''), ',', ''), 1, 8)))) || REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(LOWER(dbms_random.string('x', 5)), '0', '4'), '1', '7'), 'o', 'w'), 'l', 'k'), 'u', 'g'), 'v', 'b') END as USERNAME, X.FULLNAME, X.EMAIL, X.ROLEID, X.CUSTOMERID, (SELECT ADMINID FROM ADMIN_DIM WHERE IS_CURRENT_ADMIN='Y' ) AS ADMINID FROM (SELECT DISTINCT ORG_NODE_DIM.ORG_NODEID as ORG_NODEID, ORG_NODE_DIM.ORG_NODE_NAME as FULLNAME, ORG_NODE_DIM.EMAILS as EMAIL, ORG_NODE_DIM.CUSTOMERID AS CUSTOMERID, ORG_USER_DEFINE_LOOKUP.ROLEID, ORG_USER_DEFINE_LOOKUP.USER_SEQ, ORG_USER_DEFINE_LOOKUP.ORG_NODE_LEVEL, ORG_USER_DEFINE_LOOKUP.USER_NAME FROM ORG_NODE_DIM, ORG_USER_DEFINE_LOOKUP WHERE ORG_NODE_DIM.ORG_NODE_LEVEL = ORG_USER_DEFINE_LOOKUP.ORG_NODE_LEVEL AND ORG_NODE_DIM.CUSTOMERID = (SELECT DISTINCT CUSTOMER_ID FROM STG_ORG_NODE_DIM) AND ORG_USER_DEFINE_LOOKUP.CUSTOMERID = (SELECT DISTINCT CUSTOMER_ID FROM STG_ORG_NODE_DIM)) X ----ORDER BY X.ORG_NODEID
